WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:04.300
Imagine the brief with gravity turned off.

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:14.683
No budgets. No approvals. No clocks. Only consequence-free ambition learning to glow.

00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:22.933
The system stops negotiating with limits and begins composing with them as if they were myths.

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:33.217
What remains is pure intent: vast, lucid, impossible, and suddenly buildable.

